high_descs: Begin walking across the room to the fridge, then hang a right and walk over to the window.
Pick up the sweet potato that is on the counter in front of the window.
Turn around and walk up to the stove, then look up.
Open the microwave and place the sweet potato inside to the right of the apple, microwave the sweet potato for a couple seconds then remove it and close the microwave door.
Turn around and begin walking to the door on the other side of the room, then hang a right and walk up to the small black shelving unit in the corner of the room.
Place the heated sweet potato on the top of the small black shelving unit to the left of the bottle of lotion.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated potato on top of a small shelving unit.

high_descs: Walk forward almost to the counter then turn right and walk to the dishwasher.
Get the potato that's to the right of the salt.
Turn around and walk to the stove that's on your right.
Cook the potato in the microwave then get it out and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the door then turn right and walk to the table.
Put the potato under the salt shaker and slightly to the right.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved potato on a black table.

high_descs: Go straight, toward the fridge, then turn right to go toward the dishwasher.
Pick up the egg on the counter, to the left of the toaster.
Turn around, go straight, then turn right toward the stove, then look up at the microwave.
Cook the egg in the microwave.
Turn around, then go straight, then turn right at the door, then go to the table.
Put the egg on the table, in front of the mug.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked egg on the table.
